6750#include "llvm/Support/Debug.h"
6751#include "llvm/Support/raw_ostream.h"
6752
6753// ParseSubtargetFeatures - Parses features string setting specified
6754// subtarget options.
6755void llvm::HexagonSubtarget::ParseSubtargetFeatures(StringRef CPU, StringRef TuneCPU, StringRef FS) {
6756 LLVM_DEBUG(dbgs() << "\nFeatures:" << FS);
6757 LLVM_DEBUG(dbgs() << "\nCPU:" << CPU);
6758 LLVM_DEBUG(dbgs() << "\nTuneCPU:" << TuneCPU << "\n\n");
6759 InitMCProcessorInfo(CPU, TuneCPU, FS);
6760 const FeatureBitset &Bits = getFeatureBits();
6761 if (Bits[Hexagon::ArchV5] && HexagonArchVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V5) HexagonArchVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V5;
6762 if (Bits[Hexagon::ArchV55] && HexagonArchVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V55) HexagonArchVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V55;
6763 if (Bits[Hexagon::ArchV60] && HexagonArchVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V60) HexagonArchVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V60;
6764 if (Bits[Hexagon::ArchV62] && HexagonArchVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V62) HexagonArchVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V62;
6765 if (Bits[Hexagon::ArchV65] && HexagonArchVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V65) HexagonArchVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V65;
6766 if (Bits[Hexagon::ArchV66] && HexagonArchVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V66) HexagonArchVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V66;
6767 if (Bits[Hexagon::ArchV67] && HexagonArchVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V67) HexagonArchVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V67;
6768 if (Bits[Hexagon::ExtensionAudio]) UseAudioOps = true;
6769 if (Bits[Hexagon::ExtensionHVX] && HexagonHVXVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V60) HexagonHVXVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V60;
6770 if (Bits[Hexagon::ExtensionHVX64B]) UseHVX64BOps = true;
6771 if (Bits[Hexagon::ExtensionHVX128B]) UseHVX128BOps = true;
6772 if (Bits[Hexagon::ExtensionHVXV60] && HexagonHVXVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V60) HexagonHVXVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V60;
6773 if (Bits[Hexagon::ExtensionHVXV62] && HexagonHVXVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V62) HexagonHVXVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V62;
6774 if (Bits[Hexagon::ExtensionHVXV65] && HexagonHVXVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V65) HexagonHVXVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V65;
6775 if (Bits[Hexagon::ExtensionHVXV66] && HexagonHVXVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V66) HexagonHVXVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V66;
6776 if (Bits[Hexagon::ExtensionHVXV67] && HexagonHVXVersion < Hexagon::ArchEnum::V67) HexagonHVXVersion = Hexagon::ArchEnum::V67;
6777 if (Bits[Hexagon::ExtensionZReg]) UseZRegOps = true;
6778 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeatureCompound]) UseCompound = true;
6779 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeatureDuplex]) EnableDuplex = true;
6780 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeatureLongCalls]) UseLongCalls = true;
6781 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeatureMemNoShuf]) HasMemNoShuf = false;
6782 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeatureMemops]) UseMemops = true;
6783 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeatureNVJ]) UseNewValueJumps = true;
6784 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeatureNVS]) UseNewValueStores = true;
6785 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeatureNoreturnStackElim]) NoreturnStackElim = true;
6786 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeaturePackets]) UsePackets = true;
6787 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeaturePreV65]) HasPreV65 = true;
6788 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeatureReservedR19]) ReservedR19 = true;
6789 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeatureSmallData]) UseSmallData = true;
6790 if (Bits[Hexagon::FeatureUnsafeFP]) UseUnsafeMath = true;
6791 if (Bits[Hexagon::ProcTinyCore] && HexagonProcFamily < TinyCore) HexagonProcFamily = TinyCore;
6792}
